data.description: Absolutely gorgeous, mid-century ranch home in the much sought after area of Carlton Groves off of McGregor. Features include three bedrooms, two full bathrooms with a large open kitchen, living room, family room and wood burning fireplace. This home boasts of stunning parquet & tile flooring throughout and original decorative details you would expect. This large corner lot is just under half an acre and is absolutely a gardeners dream. Fully fenced property is full of both lush tropical and structured planting that includes avocado, key lime, orange and mango. In addition this property is designed for a RV or boat to be stored in the rear. A recently completed designer path to the front porch and main door completes this house and makes it such the treasure that it is!
